job_description:

A New York based Engineering Company is looking for an Engineer experienced in technical translation (Russian/English). The core subject area is oil refinery and technology. The ideal candidate will also have software product knowledge. 

Job Requirements:  

- proficiency in both Russian and English; 
- proofreading other content types that need technical validation; 
- relevant translation experience in the related areas (a test/sample translation may be requested); 
- grammatical and contextual accuracy and ability to meet deadlines; 
- Bachelor's degree; 
- detail-oriented, deadline-driven, and organized; 
- knowledge of Auto-CAD. 

Contact information: 

Please email your resume and a brief cover letter showing your name and contacts. 

Thank you!
